The '''4K7 Dual Line ion engine''' was a type of [[Ion engine/Legends|ion engine]] that was manufactured by [[Cygnus Spaceworks/Legends|Cygnus Spaceworks]] for use in that company's [[Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wing/Legends|Assault Gunboat]], which saw service with the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

